===2018===
科普卡在2017賽季結束後接受了手腕手術，並表示希望能在{{link-en|2018年美國名人賽|2018 Masters Tournament}}康復以趕上比賽。但由於他表示僅有八成狀態，因此決定棄權<ref>{{cite web |url=https://thegolfnewsnet.com/ryan_ballengee/2018/03/21/brooks-koepka-2018-masters-recovering-wrist-injury-108860/ |title=Brooks Koepka to miss the 2018 Masters recovering from wrist injury |publisher=Golf News Net |first=Ryan |last=Ballengee |access-date=2018-07-28 |archive-date=2021-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321070043/https://thegolfnewsnet.com/ryan_ballengee/2018/03/21/brooks-koepka-2018-masters-recovering-wrist-injury-108860/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但他成功恢復狀態，並衛冕{{link-en|2018年美國高爾夫公開賽|2018 U.S. Open (golf)|美國公開賽}}冠軍，成為1989年{{link-en|柯蒂斯·斯特蘭奇|Curtis Strange}}之後首位衛冕美國公開賽冠軍的球手，也是迄今僅有的七次衛冕成功紀錄之一<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/jun/17/brooks-koepka-history-tommy-fleetwood-retain-us-open |title=Brooks Koepka makes history in holding off Fleetwood to retain US Open title |date=2018-06-18 |newspaper=The Guardian |first=Ewan |last=Murray |access-date=2018-06-18 |archive-date=2021-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321070043/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/jun/17/brooks-koepka-history-tommy-fleetwood-retain-us-open |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在{{link-en|2018年PGA錦標賽|2018 PGA Championship}}上獲得了自己的第三個大滿貫冠軍。科普卡因此成為第五位，以及2000年[[泰格·伍茲|泰格·伍茲]]之後第一位在同一年內獲得美國公開賽和PGA錦標賽冠軍的球手<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/aug/12/brooks-koepka-holds-off-tiger-woods-fairytale-in-us-pga |title=Brooks Koepka's nerveless display denies Tiger Woods fairytale victory |date=2018-08-13 |newspaper=The Guardian |first=Ewan |last=Murray |access-date=2018-08-15 |archive-date=2021-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321070044/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2018/aug/12/brooks-koepka-holds-off-tiger-woods-fairytale-in-us-pga |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在{{link-en|2018年萊德盃|2018 Ryder Cup}}上，科普卡的一個誤擊擊中了一位女性觀眾，導致她右眼失明<ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://people.com/sports/golf-fan-loses-eyesight-brooks-koepka/?xid=socialflow_facebook_peoplemag |title=Golf Fan Loses Sight After Ball Hits Her at Ryder Cup: It Was an 'Explosion of the Eyeball' |magazine=People |last=Zauzmer |first=Emily |date=2018-10-02 |access-date=2021-03-18 |archive-date=2021-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321070044/https://people.com/sports/golf-fan-loses-eyesight-brooks-koepka/?xid=socialflow_facebook_peoplemag |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.msn.com/en-us/sports/golf/euro-tour-to-help-fan-who-has-lost-vision-from-ball-strike/ar-BBNPInY?OCID=ansmsnnews11 |title=Euro Tour to help fan who has lost vision from ball strike |work=MSN |agency=Associated Press |date=2018-10-02 |access-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003220909/https://www.msn.com/en-us/sports/golf/euro-tour-to-help-fan-who-has-lost-vision-from-ball-strike/ar-BBNPInY?OCID=ansmsnnews11 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同樣在萊德盃上，有傳言稱科普卡和隊友[[達斯汀·約翰遜|達斯汀·約翰遜]]因一些個人問題產生爭吵，但科普卡否認這一傳言，稱「我不理解這些謠言，我們之間沒有爭吵，他是我最好的朋友之一。我們通過電話交談想法。人們喜歡製造故事並傳播故事。這是一個不實消息，並且已消失」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.espn.com/golf/story/_/id/24878430/brooks-koepka-denies-fight-dustin-johnson-heartbroken-injury-spectator |title=Brooks Koepka denies fight with Dustin Johnson, calls injury to spectator 'one of my worst days' |work=ESPN |date=2018-10-03 |accessdate=2021-03-18 |archive-date=2021-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321070044/https://www.espn.com/golf/story/_/id/24878430/brooks-koepka-denies-fight-dustin-johnson-heartbroken-injury-spectator |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2018年10月21日，科普卡贏得{{link-en|CJ盃|CJ Cup}}冠軍。這一勝利使他獲得男子高爾夫[[男子高爾夫世界排名|男子高爾夫世界排名]]第一<ref>{{cite news |title=Brooks Koepka has golf's top ranking with win in South Korea |url=https://www.apnews.com/b7ab4b6091be4cd0aa4e3f491f02d8fe |work=Associated Press |access-date=2018-10-31 |date=2018-10-21 |archive-date=2021-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321070045/https://apnews.com/b7ab4b6091be4cd0aa4e3f491f02d8fe |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===2019===
2019年5月19日，科普卡贏得[[2019年PGA錦標賽|2019年PGA錦標賽]]冠軍，成為2007年泰格·伍茲之後第一位成功衛冕者<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/may/19/brooks-koepka-wins-us-pga-dustin-johnson |title=Brooks Koepka survives mini-meltdown to retain US PGA Championship |date=2019-05-19 |newspaper=The Guardian |first=Ewan |last=Murray |access-date=2019-05-21 |archive-date=2021-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321070045/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/may/19/brooks-koepka-wins-us-pga-dustin-johnson |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的世界排名也因此重回第一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.owgr.com/news/2019/may/week-20 |title=Week 20 – Koepka Returns to World No. 1 |date=2019-05-19 |publisher=Official World Golf Ranking |accessdate=2021-03-18 |archive-date=2021-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321070050/https://www.google-analytics.com/ga.js |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 	
		
在整個2019賽季，科普卡在他參與的24項主要賽事中晉級22次，晉級率達92%。

2019年7月28日，科普卡在[[普利司通邀請賽|普利司通邀請賽]]奪冠，並因此獲得1,745,000美元獎金和温德姆Top 10挑戰獎金計劃的2,000,000美元追加獎金<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pgatour.com/news/2019/07/28/brooks-koepka-takes-out-memphis-world-golf-championships-fedex-st-jude-invitational-tpc-southwind-wyndham-rewards.html |title=Koepka takes out WGC and Wyndham Rewards |publisher=PGA Tour |first=Ben |last=Everill |date=2019-07-28 |access-date=2019-07-28 |archive-date=2021-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321070046/https://www.pgatour.com/news/2019/07/28/brooks-koepka-takes-out-memphis-world-golf-championships-fedex-st-jude-invitational-tpc-southwind-wyndham-rewards.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年8月4日，科普卡獲得怡安風險獎金挑戰的1,000,000美元獎金<ref>{{cite web |title=Wyndham Championship Round 4 updates: FedExCup, Wyndham Rewards, Aon Risk Reward Challenge |first=Helen |last=Ross |date=2019-08-04 |access-date=2019-08-05 |publisher=PGA Tour |url=https://www.pgatour.com/news/2019/08/04/wyndham-championship-final-round-updates-fedexcup-standings-wyndham-rewards-top-10-aon-risk-reward-challenge.html |archive-date=2019-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806093311/https://www.pgatour.com/news/2019/08/04/wyndham-championship-final-round-updates-fedexcup-standings-wyndham-rewards-top-10-aon-risk-reward-challenge.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。科普卡在這一年連續兩年獲得PGA年度最佳球員<ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://www.golfdigest.com/story/brooks-koepka-wins-pga-player-of-the-year-over-rory-mcilroy |magazine=Golf World |date=2019-08-26 |first=Joel |last=Beall |title=Brooks Koepka wins PGA of America Player of the Year over Rory McIlroy |access-date=2021-03-18 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201085640/https://www.golfdigest.com/story/brooks-koepka-wins-pga-player-of-the-year-over-rory-mcilroy |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

科普卡取得{{link-en|2019年總統盃|2019 Presidents Cup}}參賽資格，但因膝蓋受傷而退賽，並在2019年11月20日由[[里奇·福勒|里奇·福勒]]替補參賽<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/golf/koepka-withdraws-from-presidents-cup-replaced-by-fowler/2019/11/20/5648c3f8-0bb2-11ea-8054-289aef6e38a3_story.html |title=Koepka withdraws from Presidents Cup, replaced by Fowler |newspaper=The Washington Post |first=Doug |last=Ferguson |agency=Associated Press |date=2019-11-20 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>。

2013年開始，他的球童是里奇·埃利奧特（Ricky Elliott）<ref>{{cite web |title=Ricky Elliot, Brooks Koepka’s Caddie: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know |date=2017-06-17 |access-date=2021-03-18 |publisher=Heavy.com |url=https://heavy.com/sports/2017/06/brooks-koepka-us-open-caddie-ricky-elliot/ |archive-date=2020-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805112547/https://heavy.com/sports/2017/06/brooks-koepka-us-open-caddie-ricky-elliot/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 2020 ===
在這個賽季的大部分時間內，科普卡都受到臀部和膝蓋疼痛的困擾，並棄權了聯邦快遞盃季后賽之後的賽事<ref>{{Cite web |first=Ben |last=Morse |title=Four-time major winner Brooks Koepka ends season due to injury |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/20/golf/brooks-koepka-injury-2020-season-end-spt-intl/index.html |access-date=2020-08-20 |work=CNN |archive-date=2021-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210806090358/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/20/golf/brooks-koepka-injury-2020-season-end-spt-intl/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 2021 ===
2021年2月，科普卡獲得了鳳凰城公開賽冠軍。他在最後一天逆轉了5桿劣勢，取得了低於標準桿6桿的65桿成績。這也是他第二次獲得該賽事冠軍<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cbc.ca/sports/golf/pga-phoenix-open-final-round-feb-7-1.5905015 |title=Brooks Koepka rallies to win Phoenix Open after eagling 17 |agency=Associated Press |work=CBC |date=2021-02-07 |access-date=2021-03-18 |archive-date=2021-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211003200939/https://www.cbc.ca/sports/golf/pga-phoenix-open-final-round-feb-7-1.5905015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==個人生活==
科普卡的弟弟{{link-en|蔡斯·科普卡|Chase Koepka}}也是一位職業高爾夫球手<ref name="chase">{{cite magazine |last=Huggan |first=John |title=Chase Koepka hopes Challenge Tour experience can pay off the same way it did for big brother Brooks |url=http://www.golfdigest.com/story/chase-koepka-hopes-challenge-tour-experience-can-pay-off-the-same-way-it-did-for-big-brother-brooks |magazine=Golf Digest |access-date=2017-07-22 |date=2017-06-28 |archive-date=2021-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415091235/https://www.golfdigest.com/story/chase-koepka-hopes-challenge-tour-experience-can-pay-off-the-same-way-it-did-for-big-brother-brooks |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2019年[[紐奧良蘇黎世經典賽|紐奧良蘇黎世經典賽]]上，兩人曾搭檔參賽<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pgatour.com/tournaments/zurich-classic-of-new-orleans/past-results.html |title=Zurich Classic of New Orleans – Past Results |publisher=PGA Tour |access-date=2021-03-18 |archive-date=2021-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210831065354/https://www.pgatour.com/tournaments/zurich-classic-of-new-orleans/past-results.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。科普卡的舅公[[迪克·格羅特|迪克·格羅特]]是[[美國職業棒球大聯盟|美國職業棒球大聯盟]]球員<ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://www.golfdigest.com/story/15-things-you-need-to-know-about-brooks-koepka |title=15 Things You Need To Know About Brooks Koepka |magazine=Golf Digest |first=Stephen |last=Hennessey |date=2019-05-18 |access-date=2021-03-18 |archive-date=2021-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505224308/https://www.golfdigest.com/story/15-things-you-need-to-know-about-brooks-koepka |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

